  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study evaluates a computerized cognitive therapy in patients with Parkinson's disease who
      have a mild cognitive impairment or mild dementia. The control group is &quot;trained&quot; using
      Nintendo Wii. The main outcome parameter is a neuropsychological evaluation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
